BlueJ Checkstyle Extension
==========
This is an updated version of the BlueJ extension to use Checkstyle 8.2 with
Java 1.8 on BlueJ 4.1.1

To install, put the checkstyle.jar into the extension folder in the BlueJ
directory and restart BlueJ


This directory contains the distribution for BlueJ Checkstyle Extension.
It is a tool for checking Java source code for adherence to a set of rules.

Documentation is available in HTML format, in the docs/ directory.

